The best relationships inspire you to become yourself, without changing you into someone else.

At Match, we constantly strive on updating our app to suite to your needs. Download the latest app and make a connection today!

There will be griefs and ruins but there will be a miracle. You just have to be ready to look for it.

At Match, we constantly strive to make the finding love the easiest goals to accomplish. Download the latest app today to make a connection and find that someone special.

What does knowing you found the right person on Match feel like? It's like something from an old movie, where the sailor sees the girl across the crowded dance floor, turns to his buddy and says, “See that girl? I’m gonna marry her someday.”

At Match we constantly strive to make finding love the easiest goal to accomplish. Download the latest app to make a connection and find that someone special today!

You deserve the kind of love that makes you feel like it’ll burst your veins. The kind of love that you frustrate yourself over because there isn’t a word grand enough to encompass and convey all the feelings it stirs inside of you. You deserve big love. Big, big love.

At Match, we constantly strive to make finding love the easiest goal to accomplish. Download the latest app to make a connection and find that someone special today!

Match is upping the dating game in a big way with our new feature, Match Stories.

By combining video, your voice, and your photos, Match Stories brings your profile to life by giving you the chance to showcase your personality in a more interactive way. Instead of leaving your profile static, show potential connections more of who you are and what you’re about by adding engaging video to the top of your page.

Match Stories: Your story, told by you.

Imagine finding someone who understood even the dustiest corners of your moods.

Join Match today to find that someone special. At Match, we constantly strive to make the app better and easier for you to find love. Download the latest app today and make a connection!
You’re ready to find that person, and we’re ready to help you. Download the latest version of Match today to make your search for someone special even easier.
If this wasn’t your year for love, fear not! A new one is just ahead. Download the latest version of Match today and ring in the New Year with the possibility of finding that someone special.

Thanks for using Match! We appreciate all of your feedback and ratings. To provide a better experience, we fixed a ton of bugs that were reported by our users.
- Fix for a crash occurring for some users related to uploading/managing photos
- Fix for a crash occurring for some users related to daily matches
- Ability to change gender preferences in profile edit

Thanks for using Match! We appreciate all of your feedback and ratings. To provide a better experience, we fixed a ton of bugs that were reported by our users. In this update, we:
- Fixed layouts for iPhone X to enhance the user interface
- Fixed user-reported bugs
- Improved stability to increase the performance of the app

1. Apply new filters on your Inbox
2. View only unread messages

4. Send instant replies from a chat window

We’re always working to make the Match app an even better experience for you. Download the latest version today! Below are our most recent updates:
• Daily Matches are back to full-screen glory
• Start conversations more easily with a full-screen initiation view

There’s still time to heat up your summer connections! Download the latest version of Match today to make your search for someone special even easier. Below are our most recent updates:
• We now better handle when your new set of Daily Matches come in.
• Folks now need to have a visible profile to rate matches. We agree - it's annoying when you can't see who likes you!

We’re always working to make the Match app an even better experience for you. Download the latest version today!

Our latest release focuses on fixing crashes around messaging. Bugs, be gone!

A new season means a new reason to make your Match experience even better. Download the latest version today! Below are our latest updates:
- Back by popular demand, you can again see enlarged photos in the gallery view for your Matches.
- Smart inbox is better than ever with a two-tab layout that lets you navigate messages more easily.

We’ve completely reimagined Match. With a totally new look, streamlined design and thoughtful user experience, we’ve made it easier than ever to find your someone special. Download the latest version today.

• Bug fixes and performance improvements

•3, 6, and 12-month Premium Members can now view their available perks and benefits in one place! Find the new area by visiting Profile in the bottom navigation.

This release brings further enhancements to help you get more out of your Match experience:

•The profile gets a makeover! Members can tell a better story of who they are with our redesigned profile.
•Members can now delete likes from their Likes Inbox
•New Bug fixes

- Fixed customer care contact information

Feeling lucky? We sure are. At Match, we’re always making improvements to better your experience. With this update, we’re launching a new and improved redesign of the way you edit your profile. You can now add the following information to your profile.

- Add unique Q&A topics to your profile
- Include your work information
- Share your hometown
This update includes fixes related to login bugs.

Changes in this version include:
- Ability to upload photos from Instagram
- Bug fixes to profile edit and profile view
